		<div class="comment-body"><p>Finally found the settings&#8230;<br />
u was right&#8230; now everythings works and i do get the swc and there are no more compile failures.</p>
<p>For others:<br />
&#8220;Select File &gt; Publish Settings and then select the Flash tab.<br />
Select the ActionScript version from the pop-up menu&#8221; then click the tool and change the path to dict platformer thats it <img src="http://www.wildbunny.co.uk/blog/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>
<p><a href="http://help.adobe.com/en_US/flash/cs/using/WS3e7c64e37a1d85e1e229110db38dec34-7fa4a.html" rel="nofollow">http://help.adobe.com/en_US/flash/cs/using/WS3e7c64e37a1d85e1e229110db38dec34-7fa4a.html</a></p>
<p>greets henning</p>
